            <description><![CDATA[<h2>Version 3.3.3</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Fixed: right-click menu items disappearing after automatic updates.</strong> When an update installed silently in the background, macOS could lose track of the Finder extension until the app was next opened. The app now re-registers the extension automatically after every update.</li>
    <li>If your "Convert to M4A" right-click items are currently missing, just open JessOS ADM Convert once — they'll come right back.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
