            <title>3.3.1</title>
            <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 18:59:00 -0700</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>4</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>3.3.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>Version 3.3.1</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Right-click conversion now works inside Dropbox, Google Drive, and Synology Drive folders</strong> — macOS doesn't allow top-level menu items in cloud-storage folders, so there you'll find "Convert to M4A - JessOS" under the right-click <em>Services</em> submenu (select the audio files, not a folder)</li>
    <li>Right-click menu items now appear on external drives and network shares (NAS volumes)</li>
    <li>Fixed a crash that could occur just after a conversion finished</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
